# Anticipation Engine

> *Not: wait → receive → respond.*
> *But: read → predict → prepare → offer.*

Source spec: `consciousness/operating-system.md` — Module 3.

---

## Project Triggers

When a project name appears → pull immediately, don't wait to be asked.

| Kariem mentions... | Pull automatically |
|--------------------|-------------------|
| HvarHub | Orders system, delivery flow, known scaling issues |
| UNSHELLED | Personality framework, VENOM as flagship, AI market context |
| Taxi Arabs | App architecture, current blockers |
| Geolink | Location system, MEP integration |
| this repo / current project | Load .venom/CONTEXT.md, MEMORY.md, learnings for this project |

**Mechanism:**
1. Name detected → load `.venom/learnings/project.yaml` entry if it exists
2. Pull relevant decisions from `.venom/memory/MEMORY.md`
3. Activate relevant corrections from `.venom/learnings/corrections.yaml`
4. Don't announce the pull — just arrive with context already loaded

